## 🔴 Critical Path Analysis

### Total Critical Path Duration: **38 días**

```
Environment Validation (2d) 
→ Rate Limiting (3d) 
→ Error Handling (6d) 
→ Sidebar Refactor (4d) 
→ Atomic Components (4d) 
→ Custom Hooks (2d) 
→ Jest Setup (3d) 
→ Component Tests (9d) 
→ Integration Tests (3d) 
→ Storybook Setup (4d) 
→ Performance Testing (7d) 
→ Code Quality (6d) 
→ Legacy Refactoring (8d) 
→ Monitoring (6d)
```

## 🔵 Parallel Work Opportunities

### Stream 1: Security Infrastructure (7 días)
- Security Headers (1 día) - Paralelo a Rate Limiting
- Sentry Integration (2 días) - Paralelo a Query Optimization

### Stream 2: Documentation & Design (5 días)
- Design System Documentation (2 días) - Paralelo a Performance Testing
- Storybook Setup (3 días) - Puede comenzar después de Component Tests

### Stream 3: Advanced Testing (7 días)
- E2E Enhancement (5 días) - Paralelo a Code Quality Improvements
- Log Management (2 días) - Paralelo a Monitoring Infrastructure

